short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A simple extension that adds additional details to tenders.gov.au

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension adds some additional data to the user views of the tenders.gov.au pages. Developed to enhance the user experience, provide additional transparency and generally provide a happier experience to consumers of that data within the creative commons framework. We are always interested in hearing from users on what additional features might be useful, so please get in touch. 

Ver 1.1 brings a useful feature that allows users to download to excel. Suggestions and feature requests are always welcome.
